src:
BTS’s Jungkook’s ever popular BT21 character Cooky is a struggle to get despite tons of restocking
02 Nov 2019, 12:11 by dose-nel



Jungkook has been names as a sold out king by media and fans alike, likewise character Cooky is no stranger to being sold out too! Fans have been eagerly waiting to get the cooky for slippers but it's a struggle to get since despite being restocked several times, it's still sold out. Fans everywhere are in awe of Jungkook’s insane selling power.
